{
  "transcript_id": "10549.4",
  "source_file": "10549.4.json",
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "chunk_words_setting": 800,
  "n_chunks": 4,
  "sentences": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I got my ration card, and we went to the city hall, just because I spoke very good German, I demand things.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the German people at that time, they were very-- actually [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they were-- they felt guilty because they knew what they did to us.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they tried to make it good, or at least to show that they want to make good.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the mayor, because there was a little small town, and we were, my friend and I, we were the only actually survivors who came to that little town.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were novelty.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because we were a novelty, they tried to give us the best.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After we were for about a month, after we lived there for a month in that rooming house, we demand a better headquarter-- a better-- better rooms.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sure enough, they gave us-- they gave us a-- a room in somebody's apartment.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it was much more comfortable and nicer.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we felt more of a sudden like human being again.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They gave us a ration card, and they gave us also clothing.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they gave us some money, too.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave us some money to buy the clothing.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't need-- have any money, but we had some money.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in that little town, after we were liberated, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I met some American captain.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Liberation"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was from Brooklyn.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Liberation"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He gave me a little prayer book with his-- and he ins-- he put his name on.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Goldberg.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after-- actually, after the liberation, after I was liberated, I developed-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I got [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] pleurisy.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health",
        "Liberation"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to a hospital.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He took me to a hospital, the captain.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave me good care.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I recuperated.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the first couple-- couple weeks, I mean, after the liberation.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Liberation"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that captain introduced me to a couple American soldiers.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Liberation"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the American soldiers had a lot of German money because everybody thought that the German money would be-- wouldn't be worth anything.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they gave us some German money, which to them was nothing because they couldn't buy anything out of it.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was just like a paper, like paper.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he says, They gave it to us.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Says you might be able to use it.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you might-- And we just happened to use that money to buy our self clothes because we got it.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we've become people all of a sudden.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We become person.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after we came to our self, we decide to look around.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we heard that in not far away from the place where we were was a camp with a lot of Jewish people there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the camp was Belsen-Bergen.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the concentration camp.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then it be--",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the Belsen-Bergen.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Become a DP camp, yes.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What it was, they moved from the concentration camp-- right next to the concentration camp was army barracks, was a base, actually, army base.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was air force or something like that.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, and they moved the people from that concentration camp to those barracks in where the German soldiers used to be, which was comfortable.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that become a DP camp.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the name was the same.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was Belsen-Bergen.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So when we--",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually in German, you say Belsen-Bergen.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In English, you say Bergen-Belsen, the same that-- but that's the reason why because Bergen was a little town, and Belsen was the next town.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they was right next to each other, and they called it together Belsen-Bergen.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what it was.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But are actually are two little separate towns.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that's the name.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's the name what everybody knows it, Belsen-Bergen.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And maybe the concentration camp wasn't Belsen.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And later on, the DP was in Bergen and be-- maybe that was the-- that's what it, I think it was.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we found out that there was a-- a group of Jewish people not far, that was like 50 miles away, we managed to hitchhike because everybody was hitchhiking that time, whatever [INAUDIBLE].",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the people used to take out of, what it was, army vehicles or private vehicles, whatever trucks, mostly trucks.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to jump on the trucks, and they used to hitchhike on the trucks.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we finally wound up in Belsen-Bergen.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a lot of people over there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the first thing, what it was, we were looking for somebody which we knew.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And who we came across?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I came across of my future wife.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What was her name?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was Lola, Lola [?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gertler. ?] And we were looking for somebody, somebody familiar because somebody from-- from-- from our town or somebody who we had some-- something in common.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I found out that she was there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I found her.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we found a few other people which we were together in that-- in-- in Krakow in the prison.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we met because the fellow who I was with him, he was with me in that prison too.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's why we were staying together.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were buddies.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he met somebody, or also from the-- from that prison, and we become friends because we had something in common.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I decide ask my wife-- not my future wife at that time.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, I told her, I said that your condition in the DP camp are not so good.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe you want to come to our town where we are, and maybe I can manage for you to get some clothing because we had some in in that particular town.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she decide to go with me.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I managed to buy her some clothing because you couldn't buy anything in there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the stores were closed.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no-- no-- no shopping or something.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't go in.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything was on the ration-- ration cards.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And even the stores, what they had, sell-- that were selling for it on the ration cards didn't have much of anything.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But because I knew somebody in that little town, so I managed to buy her a wardrobe.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we got a little more friendlier And-- and we decide to get married after awhile.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How long did you know her before you got married?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, almost a year before we got married.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The wedding, we decided to get married.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we had to make it legal.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were going to Frankfurt am Main because we registered already to go.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We found out Lillian-- my wife found out that she's got relatives in the-- in the United State.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we decide to go-- come to-- to America.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we registered in Frankfurt am Main to go to America.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "United States open up a quota because in order to come to the United States, every country has a quota.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So many-- at-- at that time.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how it's today, but that's how it was then.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you were born, let's say, in England, you had a quota.",
